| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4574 — Recovery Inhibition (donex)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8b9f40aa-4011-5b3a-83a7-5ff7ecdd3eb9"
